{"format": "tiptap/v1", "updatedAt": "2026-06-22T04:22:00.642Z", "doc": {"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Machine Learning (ML)"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is a subset of AI focused on algorithms that analyze training data, learn patterns from it, and make accurate inferences or predictions about new data without being explicitly programmed for each task."}]}, {"type": "blockquote", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Formal definition (Tom M. Mitchell):"}, {"type": "text", "text": " “A computer program is said to learn from experience "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "italic"}], "text": "E"}, {"type": "text", "text": " with respect to some class of tasks "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "italic"}], "text": "T"}, {"type": "text", "text": " and performance measure "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "italic"}], "text": "P"}, {"type": "text", "text": " if its performance at tasks in "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "italic"}], "text": "T"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", as measured by "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "italic"}], "text": "P"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", improves with experience "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "italic"}], "text": "E"}, {"type": "text", "text": ".”"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Arthur Samuel’s original (1959):"}, {"type": "text", "text": " “A computer’s ability to learn without being explicitly programmed.”"}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"src": "data:image/svg+xml;base64,", "alt": "Machine Learning — concept overview"}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "ML in the hierarchy: AI → ML → DL → Gen AI"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Machine Learning sits between AI and Deep Learning:"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "text"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "AI (Artificial Intelligence)\n └── ML (Machine Learning)\n      └── DL (Deep Learning)\n           └── Gen AI (Generative AI, often built on DL)"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "AI"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Any system that mimics human intelligence (rule-based, search, planning, ML, etc.)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "ML"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": AI that "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "italic"}], "text": "learns from data"}, {"type": "text", "text": " using statistical algorithms"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "DL"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": A specialized form of ML using deep neural networks"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Gen AI"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": AI that "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "italic"}], "text": "creates new content"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (text, images, code), typically using deep learning models like transformers"}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Classical Machine Learning vs. Generative AI"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Within ML, there are two major paradigms:"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Aspect"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Classical (Traditional) Machine Learning"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Generative AI"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Goal"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Predict, classify, cluster, or regress on existing data"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Generate "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "italic"}], "text": "new"}, {"type": "text", "text": " data samples that resemble training data"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Type"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Mostly "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "discriminative"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (learns boundaries between classes)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Generative"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (learns full data distribution to sample new examples)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Typical output"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Label, score, or numeric prediction (e.g., “fraud”, price, probability)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "New content: text, image, audio, video, code"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Common algorithms"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Linear/logistic regression, SVM, Decision Trees, Random Forests, Gradient Boosting (XGBoost, LightGBM), K-Means"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Transformers (LLMs), GANs, Diffusion models, VAEs"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Data type"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Mostly "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "structured/tabular"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", often labeled (supervised)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Mostly "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "unstructured"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (text, images), often self-supervised/unsupervised"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Learning style"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Primarily supervised; some unsupervised & reinforcement"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Often unsupervised or self-supervised pre-training"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Use cases"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Fraud detection, spam filters, sales forecasting, customer segmentation, churn prediction"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Chatbots (ChatGPT), AI art (DALL·E, Midjourney), code generation, synthetic data"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Resources"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Faster training, runs on CPUs, easier to deploy, cheaper at scale"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Heavy training, GPU/cluster required, large models, more complex"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Interpretability"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "More interpretable, easier to explain"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Less interpretable, “black box”"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Mental model"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Classical ML = analyst"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": classifies, predicts, and analyzes data based on patterns."}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Generative AI = creator"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": learns from existing data and then creates entirely new content."}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Why classical ML still matters in the age of Gen AI"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even with Gen AI dominating headlines, classical ML remains the backbone of many production systems:"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Most real-world AI systems still rely heavily on traditional ML"}, {"type": "text", "text": " for tasks like:"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "- Logistic Regression - Random Forests - Gradient Boosting (XGBoost, LightGBM) - Support Vector Machines\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "On tabular data"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", tree-based classical models often "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "outperform"}, {"type": "text", "text": " deep/generative models, especially with less data and far less computation.\n- Classical ML models: - Train faster - Run on CPUs - Are easier to deploy and maintain - Scale cheaply"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The future is "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "hybrid systems"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Generative AI adds a layer of intelligence and creativity, while classical ML does the heavy lifting for predictions, classifications, and structured-data tasks."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Key takeaways"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "ML"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is the AI subset that learns patterns from data to make predictions or decisions without explicit task-by-task programming."}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Classical ML"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is primarily discriminative: classification, regression, clustering on structured data."}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Generative AI"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is generative: it creates new content (text, images, code) by learning the data distribution."}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Classical ML is still essential for enterprise analytics, tabular data, and cost-effective, interpretable models."}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Gen AI "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "stands on the shoulders"}, {"type": "text", "text": " of classical ML and deep learning; it doesn’t replace them but complements them."}]}]}]}]}}